    "text": "Jakarta’s 2026 tech scene is still anchored by a dense digital and fintech ecosystem, with events such as ASOCIO Digital AI Summit 2026 and Jakarta Fintech Connect 2026 reflecting active industry networking and AI/fintech collaboration in the city. The presence of infrastructure-focused gatherings like the Indonesia Cloud & Datacenter Convention also points to continued demand for cloud, data-center, and digital-economy services. For freelancers, this environment supports ongoing needs in software development, design, and digital marketing, especially for companies working across fintech, AI, and transformation projects, while remote and outsourced collaboration remains relevant in Indonesia’s digital economy.",
