    "text": "Cebu’s tech and digital ecosystem in 2026 is shaped by its role as a major Philippine regional job center, with demand spread across IT, digital services, and BPO-related work. The local market also reflects the broader presence of outsourcing and remote work, as companies increasingly hire Philippine talent for software development, data, digital marketing, and project-management roles. Freelance openings on major platforms and job boards continue to include IT support and data-focused work, while the wider freelance market also supports design and marketing tasks tied to digital operations.",
