    "text": "Phnom Penh’s tech scene in 2026 is still developing, but recent reports describe a growing startup ecosystem supported by programs such as Khmer Enterprise and Startup Cambodia, along with international partnerships like Plug and Play Cambodia and La French Tech Phnom Penh. The city’s business base includes fintech, digital platforms, and SME-oriented innovation, with Cambodia’s startup ecosystem ranked 105th globally in the 2026 Global Startup Ecosystem Index. For freelancers, that environment points to continued demand for software, design, and digital marketing work, while remote-work and outsourcing links remain important as local firms connect to regional and international markets.",
